name: Pickled Mango

reviews.review_text: We came from Belgaum to celebrate my son's 1st Birthday in Resort Rio. The Resort was beautiful well maintained. Mr Francisco the Restaurant Manager has made a wonderful set-up by the pool to celebrate our son's Birthday. We got very good service in the pickled mango Restaurant. Thanks Resot Rio.

Brilliant food and amazing service. The manager Bosco and Sahil made us feel very comfortable. Crispin who served us throughout was just fantastic and very attentive. All of them were so polite, friendly and smiley at all times. We thoroughly enjoyed our evening celebrating our wedding anniversary. Would highly recommend visiting this restaurant and having a great evening.

Pickled Mango was a delicious experience for our mornings during the stay in Resort Rio.
The staff is impeccable and ever smiling.
Thank you so much for the amazing hospitality.
Special thanks to Mr. Dilip for his sweet gestures that made our breakfast experience even more lovely.

description:
**Pickled Mango: A Culinary Gem at Resort Rio, Goa**

Nestled within the serene confines of Resort Rio, just a stone’s throw from Goa University, Pickled Mango shines brightly in the culinary landscape, boasting an impressive 5.0 rating from 1,178 enthusiastic reviewers. Celebrated for its top-notch service and delightful cuisine, the restaurant has become a favored destination for both locals and tourists. Recurring themes among customer feedback highlight its inviting atmosphere and exceptional hospitality, making it a perfect spot for celebrations, be it a birthday or an anniversary.

**Ambiance & Design**

From the moment you step into Pickled Mango, a warm and inviting ambiance envelops you, enhanced by the elegant décor and strategic lighting that reflects the Goan charm. Photos of the restaurant reveal a delightful setup, particularly the stunning poolside arrangements where guests can enjoy their meals surrounded by lush greenery. The inviting atmosphere is complemented by the ever-smiling staff, creating a space that is as visually pleasing as it is welcoming. The sound of laughter mingles with gentle music, creating a lively yet relaxed environment—ideal for both intimate dinners and larger gatherings.

**Menu & Culinary Experience**

The culinary offerings at Pickled Mango are as diverse as they are delectable, earning high praise for their delicious flavor profiles and presentation. Although specific dishes are not detailed in the reviews, the collective sentiment underscores a memorable dining experience, especially during breakfast, which is highlighted as a delightful treat by returning guests. Diners appreciate the attention to detail in both the taste and presentation of the dishes, with one customer specifically recognizing the sweet gestures of the staff that elevated the entire experience.

**Customer Experience & Service**

Exceptional service is a common thread throughout customer reviews, with guests frequently commending the attentiveness and friendliness of the staff. Manager Bosco, alongside team members Sahil and Crispin, have been singled out for their exemplary service, ensuring every guest feels valued and comfortable. The presence of Mr. Dilip, whose hospitable nature was noted during a breakfast visit, further enhances the sense of personalized service that Pickled Mango strives to offer. This commitment to customer satisfaction extends to a well-coordinated reservation system, ensuring a seamless dining experience, whether you’re planning a special occasion or a casual meal.

**Popularity & Reviews**

With a remarkable reputation bolstered by numerous accolades, Pickled Mango has garnered significant attention on social media platforms. Customers consistently share their glowing reviews, emphasizing not just the food but the welcoming environment. The restaurant's connection to Resort Rio adds an extra layer of allure, positioning it as an ideal dining choice for guests of the resort and visitors alike. The awards and recognition achieved further solidify its status as a must-visit culinary destination in Goa.

**Utilizing Visual Content**

Incorporating visual elements into the dining experience, the shared photos from patrons showcase enticing dishes and the appealing atmosphere of Pickled Mango. From beautifully plated meals to snapshots of the enchanting poolside setup, the visuals bring the reviews to life, offering a glimpse into what guests can expect when they choose this remarkable restaurant.

In conclusion, Pickled Mango is not just a restaurant; it’s a delightful escape for those seeking a blend of delectable food, exceptional service, and a serene atmosphere. Whether you're celebrating a special occasion or simply looking to indulge in a truly enjoyable dining experience, Pickled Mango at Resort Rio is the destination worth visiting time and again.
